<div class="header">
    <h1>React Tasks</h1>
    <img src="/images/react.gif" alt="react"/> 
</div>
<div class="task">
    <h2>Task 1</h2>
    <p>Create a calculator on React.</p>
    <ul>
        <li> The calculator should have all working functionality</li>
        <li>implement good design</li>
        <li>after completing the calculator project deploy it on github.</li>
        <li>host it on netlify or some other</li>
        <li>submit the link of the hosted website and github repository on the below submission form</li>
         <li>Marks: 20/100.</li>
    </ul>
</div>
<div class="task">
    <h2>Task 2</h2>
    <p>React Weather website.</p>
    <ul>
        <li>the Weather app should display the weather according to the searched location</li>
        <li>the weather app should have a good design and animations </li>
        <li>the weather app should have a good UI</li>
        <li>use available api to fetch weather data according to the location(hint: use apis from Rapid API)</li>
        <li>after completing the weather app project deploy it on github.</li>
        <li>host it on netlify or some other hosting platform</li>
        <li>submit the link of the hosted website and github repository on the below submission form</li>
        <li>Marks: 30/100</li>
    </ul>
</div>
<div class="task">
    <h2>Task 3</h2>
    <p>Netflix Clone in React.</p>
    <ul>
        <li>create a netfils clone the frontend should be in react and in Backend use FireBase</li>
        <li>the netflix clone should have a good looking visuals, you can also give your own touch </li>
        <li>Impliment only the basic functionality of netflix like home page, Search bar, sign-in page, sign-up page, browse page, and movie player page.</li>
        <li>after completing the project deploy it on github.</li>
        <li>host it on netlify or some other hosting platform</li>
        <li>submit the link of the hosted website and github repository on the below submission form</li>
        <li>Max Marks: 50/100</li>
       
    </ul>
</div>
<div class="task-submission">
    <h2>Task Submission</h2>
    <form id="taskSubmissionForm" action="/submit-task" method="POST">
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label for="name" class="form-label">Name</label>
        <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Enter your name" required>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label for="email" class="form-label">Email</label>
        <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label for="task" class="form-label">Task</label>
        <select class="form-select" id="task" name="task" required>
          <option value="">Select a task</option>
          <option value="Task 1">Task 1 - Create a calculator on React</option>
          <option value="Task 2">Task 2 - React Weather website</option>
          <option value="Task 3">Task 3 - Netflix Clone on React</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label for="githubLink" class="form-label">GitHub Repository Link</label>
        <input type="url" class="form-control" id="githubLink" name="githubLink" placeholder="Enter the GitHub repository link" required>
      </div>
      <div class="mb-3">
        <label for="hostedLink" class="form-label">Hosted Website Link</label>
        <input type="url" class="form-control" id="hostedLink" name="hostedLink" placeholder="Enter the hosted website link" required>
      </div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
    </form>
</div>
  
